@startuml
title Memoria Conversazionale - Opzione MongoDB (Sequence)

actor       Studente         as S
participant "Frontend\n(App.jsx)"             as FE
participant "POST /api/agent/query\n(main.py)" as API
participant "OrchestratorAgent"               as ORC
participant "ConversationRepository\n(MongoDB)" as REPO
database    "MongoDB\nconversations"          as MDB

' ─── Login + carica chat precedenti ──────────────────────────
S -> FE : login
FE -> API : POST /api/auth/login
API --> FE : JWT cookie + userInfo

FE -> API : GET /api/conversations
API -> REPO : getConversations(matricola)
REPO -> MDB : find({ matricola })\nsorted by updatedAt desc
MDB --> REPO : lista conversazioni
REPO --> API : [{ id, title, updatedAt }, ...]
API --> FE : lista conversazioni

FE --> S : mostra sidebar con chat precedenti

' ─── Studente apre/crea una chat ─────────────────────────────
alt nuova conversazione
  S -> FE : click "Nuova chat"
  FE -> API : POST /api/conversations\n{ matricola }
  API -> REPO : createConversation(matricola)
  REPO -> MDB : insertOne\n{ matricola, messages:[], createdAt }
  MDB --> REPO : { conv_id }
  REPO --> API : { conv_id }
  API --> FE : { conv_id }
else riapre conversazione esistente
  S -> FE : click su chat precedente
  FE -> API : GET /api/conversations/{conv_id}
  API -> REPO : getMessages(conv_id)
  REPO -> MDB : findOne({ _id: conv_id })
  MDB --> REPO : { messages[] }
  REPO --> API : messages[]
  API --> FE : messages[]
  FE --> S : mostra storico conversazione
end

' ─── Turno N ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
S -> FE : invia messaggio

FE -> API : POST /api/agent/query\n{ query, user_info, conv_id }

API -> REPO : getRecentHistory(conv_id, limit=10)
REPO -> MDB : findOne({ _id: conv_id })\nslice messages -10
MDB --> REPO : ultimi 10 msg
REPO --> API : conversation_history[]

API -> ORC : process_query(query, user_info, conv_repo, conv_id)

ORC -> ORC : crea AgentState\n{ query, conversation_history, user_info, ... }
ORC -> ORC : Classifier → Generator → Revisor\n(invariati)
ORC -> ORC : final_response pronto

ORC -> REPO : appendMessages(conv_id, user_msg, assistant_msg)
REPO -> MDB : updateOne({ _id: conv_id })\n$push messages user_msg\n$push messages assistant_msg\n$set updatedAt = now()

note over REPO, MDB
  Ogni messaggio viene scritto
  direttamente su MongoDB —
  nessun rischio di perdita dati
  in caso di crash o chiusura browser.
end note

ORC --> API : { response, metadata }
API --> FE : { response, metadata }
FE --> S : mostra risposta

legend bottom
  | Aspetto              | Comportamento                              |
  | Fonte della history  | MongoDB (lato server)                     |
  | Payload dal client   | query + user_info + conv_id               |
  | Scadenza sessione    | nessuna — storico permanente              |
  | Persistenza storico  | scrittura ad ogni messaggio               |
  | Conversazioni multi  | sì — gestite tramite conv_id              |
  | AgentState           | invariato, riceve history da MongoDB      |
endlegend

@enduml
